            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 100 mines.
                Dépenses de l'année: <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 21 mines 60 oboles. 
                <supplied reason="lost">Reste</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 3 drachmes 3 oboles 1/10.
                <supplied reason="lost">Indemnité pour les démiurges</supplied> 3 mines.
            </p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 100 mines.
                Expense of the year: <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 21 mines 60 obols. 
                <supplied reason="lost">Remainder</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 3 drachmas 3 obols 1/10.
                <supplied reason="lost">Allowance for the damiergoi</supplied> 3 mines.
            </p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 100 mine.
                Totale: uscite dell'anno: <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 21 mine 60 oboli. 
                <supplied reason="lost">Resto</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 3 dracme 3 oboli 1/10.
                <supplied reason="lost">Retribuzione per i damiurghi</supplied> 3 mine.
            </p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p>[---] 100 ميناي. نفقات السنة: [---] 21 ميناي 60 أوبول. [الباقي] [---] 3 دراخما 3.1 أوبول. [تُعطى للداميرجوي] 3 ميناي.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>The values of expense and remainder are only partially preserved.</p>
	      <p>At line 1, the amount beginning with <foreign xml:lang="grc">M</foreign> for 'mine' would be, in the simplest formula, the income of the year. However, in the usual formulation, 
	          it does not include a word ending with the letter-parts still visible, which show the ending of the dative case. Therefore, <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/></bibl> is 
	      probably right in supposing that we have here the end of a detailed list of expenses, such as for instance in <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr011600</ref>.</p>
            </div></body>
